Example 3 : small sample

pvalue example
par(mfrow = c(1,1), mar=c(4,2,0.8,2))
x <- rnorm(10000)
pvalue(x, 1.96, plot = T)

## [1] 0.02552841


1) level test
round(p_level, 2)
##   x1   x2   x3   x4   x5   x6 
## 0.00 0.01 0.00 0.00 0.32 0.29


2) parallel test

\(x_1 - x_2, x_2 - x_3, ..., x_{p-1} - x_p,\;p = the\,number\,of\,variables\)

round(p_parallel, 2)
## x1-x2 x2-x3 x3-x4 x4-x5 x5-x6 
##   0.0   0.0   0.0   0.0   0.5
